Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:41.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how\Nmuch money I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:44.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without her, it doesn't mean a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:55.31,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11\NFlower Wine for Tanda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:11.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind telling me again\Nhow she seemed yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:17.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was about this time yesterday.\NShe just collapsed all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what about after she collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:24.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was no fever, and since it\Nlooked like she was just sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:29.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I assumed that the flower wine had\Ngone to her head, so I put her to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flower wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why would she\Nbe drinking flower wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:39.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was to celebrate\Na happy occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum? Did you\Ncome here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was with Balsa till\Njust before I reached the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:53.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa said she was going to look\Nfor Toya and went back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is she ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:05.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, but judging from the\Nexamination I gave her a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:08.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it's almost as if her\Nsoul has left her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:14.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean one of those out-of-body\Nexperiences one hears about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:20.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's not unusual for something\Nto trigger the soul to leave the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:24.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you're dozing off\Nand you suddenly jerk awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...because it feels like you're falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:32.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sensation is the moment\Nthat your soul leaves your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:37.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, though, the soul hurries\Nstraight back to the body, and you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We do not need\Nto worry about Saya then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:53.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the house that\NTanda rented for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he isn't here,\Nthat must mean he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like doing\Nanything at all any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel like doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fine house you're renting...\NWhy would you abandon it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:45.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in living\Nin that house all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:54.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming\Nall the way out here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:58.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come, we can discuss\Nthe particulars while we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:43.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have done such\Na fine job raising Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:46.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...even though she's\Nnot your sister by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:50.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess she's more like\Na daughter than a sister to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:55.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to pat myself on the back,\Nbut you won't find a better girl than Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite sure she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:01.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, if her\Nhappiness is your main concern...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I strongly suggest\Nthat you accept this offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, Saya's still such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, Saya is already\Na fine young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The match I have suggested\Nfor her is also a fine young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And his family is above reproach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:27.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that there is\Nno finer match to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:33.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this sum\Nas her betrothal gift money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:41.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any big brother would\Nwant his sister to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:46.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what I think doesn't matter.\NSaya hasn't agreed, so I can't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if that is your concern,\Ndo not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:55.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have already received\Na favorable response from Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:08.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking\Nsuch good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:18.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Saya's\Ncollapse and that meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...have some sort of link.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:27.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details,\Nbut that's why I came here to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A marriage was being\Narranged for Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:39.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, with the son of the rice merchant\Nwe always do business with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arranged marriages are something\Nto be happy about, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:56.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but something terrible\Nmight have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:02.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and her soul is refusing to\Nreturn to her body because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:09.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did Saya seem\Nat the marriage meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anything\Nthat struck you as odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:17.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she did seem\Nto be brooding a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening to Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I was against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was told that you\Ngave your blessing right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:00.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a good match that you\Njust charmed them into it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You lied... How could\Nyou do that to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:09.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Saya. If I'd only\Nbeen clear in turning her down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know what\Ncaused her condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:17.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...won't Saya's soul return if we\Ntell her that the marriage is off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:24.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It should, but she can't seem\Nto hear us the way she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to help her is\Nto perform a soul-summoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A soul-summoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:35.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya's soul has probably gone to\Nthe other world, so I'll send my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and bring hers back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:44.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really capable of\Ndoing something of that scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mentor did teach me how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'd like\Nto prepare for the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to ask everyone\Nto go into the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:15.01,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:31.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that no one\Ncomes into this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:36.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, if you two could\Njoin the others in the next room...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:58.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Torogai forbid you from\Never performing a soul-summoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:04.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were about\Nto jump into a well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd feel confident that\NI could pull you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:10.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't exactly\Ntie a rope to a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know the risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:15.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But since Torogai isn't here,\NI have to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:22.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll make sure\NI summon Saya's soul back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If things go wrong,\Nand I don't make it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll be watching over you at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be keeping an eye\Non you here. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:40.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Soul, spread your wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Become like a bird\Nsoaring through the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that my soul\Nhas left my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:53.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:06.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:09.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:16.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to bring you back.\NEveryone's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:21.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to agree\Nto the marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I just couldn't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NDon't worry about that any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:32.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she said that Toya would surely\Nbe punished if I didn't get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not really his sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:41.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I lied to Toya about\Nwanting to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are no grounds\Nto punish Toya for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:51.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really. And Toya is\Nsitting in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:00.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was so worried about you\Nthat he came storming in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:05.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't go back... I think I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you aren't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:15.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's it coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take her to the next room\Nand give her some hot water to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't had anything to eat\Nor drink for a day and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she made it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:22.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanda hasn't returned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His curiosity always\Ngets the better of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:30.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must be lingering on his\Nway back from the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should join the others\Nand get something to eat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on Tanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't find your\Nway back, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at my wits' end...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what\NI said to you two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...when you came back\Nall covered in blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:18.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have to take one life\Nto save another, what's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:23.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked if you were killing more\Nthan you were saving, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really mean to\Nsay that to you, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:32.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I stormed out of your\Nplace two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:36.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but looking back on it now,\NI think I was just being stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:44.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it was your words that kept me\Nfrom killing a single person since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:53.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the one\Nwho should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand now...\NHow anxious you were back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:03.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How saving the lives of others\Nchips away at your own life, bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for that, Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, what am I doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has the sun come up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nayug?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's Sagu's moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:23.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what an incredible world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:56.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So at this moment, I'm literally on\Nthe border between Nayug and Sagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanda still hasn't woken up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:11.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, are those\Nrice cakes for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really have to\Ncome up with something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It travels back and forth\Nbetween Nayug and Sagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:07.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya's out-of-body experience was\Ntriggered by drinking that flower wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I've got to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But how can I\Nmake them understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Nyunga Ro Im egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:34.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being pulled straight into\NNayug because of the egg then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:44.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this egg actually straddles the\Nborder of Nayug and Sagu, then I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to give Tanda\Nsome of that flower wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was the nectar of\Nthose flowers in the wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that caused Saya's\Nsoul to leave her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:46.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have done\Nthat a little more gently?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:12.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit, I didn't see it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:15.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, Saya is in love with Toya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:18.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:23.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. But in hindsight,\NI suppose all the signs were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:30.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:44.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a double moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:49.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that second\None was Nayug's sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:55.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Sagu and Nayug are\Ndrawn to each other during the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:57.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:45.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Founding Day Festival is held in\Nfarm villages on the summer solstice...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:45.15,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.68,0:24:49.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To defend his father's honor,\NChagum challenges a foreign boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:53.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\N"The Summer Solstice Festival."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12\NThe Summer Solstice Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.32,0:24:56.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This first act of defiance\Nforges lasting bonds.
